Synology Logo
Synology Inc. is a Taiwanese corporation that specializes in Network-attached storage appliances. Synology’s line of NAS is known as the DiskStation for desktop models, FlashStation for all-flash models, and RackStation for rack-mount models. Synology’s products are distributed worldwide and localized in several languages. Synology’s headquarters are located in Taipei, Taiwan, with subsidiaries located around the world. In 2018, product review website Wirecutter described Synology as a longtime “leader in the small-business and home NAS arena”, albeit still a newcomer in the field of Wi-Fi routers.
